text: The Phillipsburg Commercial Historic District is a historic district in Phillipsburg, Warren County, New Jersey. The district was added to the National Register of Historic Places on October 8, 2008 for its local history and representative late 19th and early 20th century commercial structures. It includes 70 contributing resources.
